descriptionHtml:
A small cabin player home located close to Riverwoood.

Features lots of named storages, some weapon racks and all crafting stations apart from a smelter.

Fully navmeshed, so followers can accompany you.

With Mapmarker, so you can fast travel to it.
This is my very first Mod, so there might be issues, just post them in the comments
